name: Velvet - Odin Sphere (Character)
description:
This is a LORA of the character Velvet from Vanillaware's Odin Sphere.

To prompt this character, enter "<lora:Velvet-OdinSphere-v1.0:strength>velvet, red hood, crop top, puffy sleeves, star hat headdress, long skirt, vertical-striped stockings, high heels,"

This LORA is usually the best looking at 0.6 ~ 0.75 strength.

Version 2 addsmore than double the images to the dataset, and increases the overall details, flexibility, and quality of the model. In addition, some training was done on Velvet's psypher weapon, although it's exceptionally difficult for it to come out as desired. I included it anyway in the case you want to try prompting it using "gem, chain, holding weapon/chain around wrist"

modelVersions.name: v2
modelVersions.description: Doubled the size of the dataset, increased detail, more flexibility! The chain weapon Velvet uses is partially trained but it is incredibly difficult to train, so I left it mostly alone for now. If you want to try prompting it, use "gem, chain, holding weapon/chain around wrist".
